/hongkongww3.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Friverflowing09.blogspot.com%2F2014%2F09%2Fhongkongww3.html%3Fm%3D1&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrsjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=9e55a5a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://riverflowing09.blogspot.com/2014/09/hongkongww3.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n中國跟俄羅斯一樣都是不好侵略的國家，如要導致中國出戰，必定要藉對付俄羅斯同樣的方法去挑釁中國。<br />\n而中國的經濟命脈地方就是香港，因為香港一直以來都是成為中國與西方國家經濟接釀的中間角色，是經濟、金融和食物轉運的港口。事實上，中國大部分金和銀都是靠香港匯豐銀行不斷運到國內。即使中國和其他國家斷絕了外交，只要藉著香港進行買賣，就可以維持整個經濟局面。故此，香港對中國經濟是極具重要性！"},{"pid":"7c752059710b1651862ae740c28c020c18903ef4","tid":1509421,"uid":258128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0c1c35917642c7e0c91e5412134ceb802e371f1","tid":1509421,"uid":127638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:01:00.000Z","msg":"哇 2062....<br />\n不過如果到當時中國都仲係急速發展國家證明左一樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:06:13.000Z","msg":"唔好係真"},{"pid":"20db3ada183a1298a066b3f27b324940e5771260","tid":1509421,"uid":294746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:11:03.000Z","msg":"美國軍事專家指出，與中國和俄羅斯的大國戰爭的雖然可能很遙遠，但是越來越真切。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/military/alkzlz6.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fmilitary%2Falkzlz6.html&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrsjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=126148ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/military/alkzlz6.html</a>"},{"pid":"df0e8e791b9f573389fde8f4ad5266e36adfb352","tid":1509421,"uid":294746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:11:47.000Z","msg":"中美若開戰，會在哪裡爆發，以什麼樣的方式開始？<br />\n美國戰略與預算評估中心麥肯認為，中美可能會因為台灣問題陷入戰爭。中國有可能對美國實施核武打擊；襲擊美軍的後勤網絡、干擾衛星定位系統，進行太空戰等。另外，中國也可能會在網絡上發起對美國的黑客戰爭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/military/alkzlz6.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fmilitary%2Falkzlz6.html&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrsjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=126148ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/military/alkzlz6.html</a>"}]}